Global Leisure Boats Market Insights
Leisure Boats Market size was valued at USD 24.35 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 39.24 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.10% from 2024 to 2030.

Leisure Boats Market Overview
The global leisure boats market has been experiencing significant growth, with a market value of approximately USD 23.5 billion in 2024 and expected to reach around USD 30.6 billion by 2028, at a CAGR of 5.5%. This growth is driven by increasing disposable income, rising demand for recreational activities, and the growing popularity of boating among young consumers. The market is segmented by type, including sailboats, motorboats, and inflatable boats, each catering to different consumer preferences. Additionally, the trend of luxury leisure boats is on the rise, attracting affluent buyers seeking high-end experiences.

